name: NativeTung
tag_list: machine-translation, localization, automated-translation, website-translation, globalization, real-time, internationalization, content-translation, translation, cms, language-translation
overview: NativeTung is an advanced language translation platform that enables websites to easily establish multilanguage content channels that maximize global audience reach and engagement online. NativeTung is pioneering the emerging real-time automated translation segment of the language translation industry. NativeTung’s proprietary technology is revolutionizing how websites – such as blogs, corporate sites, media properties, and social networks – create, analyze, and grow their international business online.
